commit.message:
Track proper indentation/column for closing 'Ann'

'SPopAnn' needs to use whatever the indentation and column positions are _after_
consuming the annotated document - it can't just use the same ones as 'SPushAnn'.
In fact, using the same ones as 'SPushAnn' will only ever work if the annotated
text has no width.

This should address #2.
